snippet.title: Aircraft In Pixels: Albatros D V
snippet.description:
New gameplay trailer for version 0.1.7 of Aircraft in Pixels 2: Albatros D.V.

Aircraft in Pixels 2: Albatros D.V is a virtual model airplane. Assemble, paint and apply decals to a realistic world war biplane -- without the fumes or the mess!

Aircraft in Pixels is now in early release at https://bomonroe.itch.io/aircraft-in-pixels-2 with introductory pricing.
